Johannesburg- The day of the ‘National Lunch Date’ is here. Mr Smeg will be taking Pearl Thusi on a date at Daruma Different brands have come in and sponsored the national lunch date for the two. The duo received some clothing items from different brands in preparation for today’s date, which is deemed as the national date. Smeg took to his socials and thanked people who have given him things to wear to his date, DJ Zinhle is one of them.          Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here